channel.title: NRS3 Server Source Running.. Error
channel.description:
Hi,
When i try and run the run.bat it comes with the next error:
Maybe someone could help me?
[code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.UnsupportedClassVersionError: com/rs/Launcher : Unsupported major.minor version 51.0 at java.lang.ClassLoader.defineClass1(Native Method) at java.lang.ClassLoader.defineClassCond(ClassLoader.java:631) at java.lang.ClassLoader.defineClass(ClassLoader.java:615) at java.security.SecureClassLoader.defineClass(SecureClassLoader.java:141) at java.net.URLClassLoader.defineClass(URLClassLoader.java:283) at java.net.URLClassLoader.access$000(URLClassLoader.java:58) at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run(URLClassLoader.java:197) at java.security.AccessController.doPrivileged(Native Method) at java.net.URLClassLoader.findClass(URLClassLoader.java:190) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(ClassLoader.java:306) at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass(Launcher.java:301) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(ClassLoader.java:247) [/code]

item.title: NRS3 Server Source Running.. Error
item.dc:creator: @EvilscapeV3 EvilscapeV3
item.description:
@EvilscapeV3 wrote:

meh this is a common problem with JDK and JRE.

The problem is you compile the server with a more recent version of JDK, and when you run it with later version it gives you this error.

What I suggest download the latest version of JDK, and compile. That should take care of your problem.
